ALCOM PROPOSES TO DISSOLVE ITSELF . Finnish data systems group Alcom said in a statement on Friday it proposed to an extraordinary shareholders meeting that it be dissolved . The meeting would be held on June 13 at 0900 local time . " The meeting will deal with the state of the company and the board ' s proposal to dissolve it by means of debt - restructuring , " Alcom said . - - Helsinki newsroom + 358 - 9 - 680 50 242 , news @ reuters . fi 
